  "lines": [
    "----",
    "",
    "",
    "Can you ask me a question with the question tool with multiple response, I mean the user can select multiple response",
    "",
    "----",
    "",
    "",
    "**󰧑  Reasoning** ",
    "",
    "The user wants to see an example of using the question tool with multiple selection enabled. I'll create a simple example question where they can select multiple options.",
    "",
    "** question** ",
    "",
    "----",
    "",
    "",
    " Question",
    "",
    "Which programming languages do you use?",
    "",
    "      1. Lua - Lua programming language ",
    "      2. Python - Python programming language",
    "      3. TypeScript - TypeScript programming language",
    "      4. Rust - Rust programming language",
    "      5. Other - Type your own answer",
    "    →  Confirm - Submit selected answers",
    "",
    "Move: `j/k` or `↑/↓`",
    "Question: `h/l` or `<-/->`",
    "Toggle/Edit: `<CR>` or `<Tab>` or `<Space>` or `1-5`",
    "Submit: select Confirm and press `<CR>`",
    "Close: `<Esc>`",
    "",
    ""
